text: Voëns-Maley is a village in the municipality of Saint-Blaise in the Swiss canton of Neuchâtel. Since 1888, it became a part of Saint-Blaise. It contains two villages: Voëns and Maley. Voëns is a golf course. == Other websites == * Category:Former municipalities of Neuchâtel Category:Villages in Neuchâtel
